{"tid":2487817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港同黃錦輝各錄10多人「抽飛」　女拔29人退學10多人插班","createTime":"2021-04-14T00:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:46:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4b97f203e57cd768fedfa3120909c2ac81e51c","tid":2487817,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uUyHjtv3deuksKa-58OeW5lI9wk=/535x356/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWJB3BERG5DDZP5AUEAZV5IFBM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuUyHjtv3deuksKa-58OeW5lI9wk%3D%2F535x356%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWJB3BERG5DDZP5AUEAZV5IFBM.JPG&h=93f80e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大同學會書院副校長陳永昌指早預計移民潮影響收生，在面試階段傾向選擇擬初中留港升學的申請者。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n移民潮掀學校「音樂椅」效應，加上自行分配學位階段提早公佈正取生結果，今年升中學生流動更添變數。港大同學會書院早預計移民潮影響退學人數，在面試階段傾向選擇擬初中留港升學的申請者，今年該校錄得十多人「抽飛」放棄直資學位轉投官津名校；直接資助學校議會主席陳狄安呼籲家長，若現階段獲不止一間直資學校取錄，應及早通知學校放棄學位。<br />\n<br />\n陳永昌：學生是否短期內離港 會計算在面試分內<br />\n港大同學會書院今年錄得十多人「抽飛」，校方指放棄學額的家長多因在自行階段獲傳統名校取錄，包括皇仁書院、英華女學校等。港同中一學額共200個，扣除預留小學部學額後，約取錄不多於80名外校生。副校長陳永昌指，今年度申請者較前年反增逾百人至1,700人，「學校已預計外在環境因素，面試分佔40%，學生是否在未來1至2年離港，確實會在面試部分計算在內」。<br />\n該校早在今年2月進行家長意向調查，預計今年退學人數較往年增3至4%；過往一直有三至四成中三以上學生往海外升學。因此，校方早年已增加中一學額至200個，以抵銷高中生流失，「不過，（今年）是多了十名學生退學，原因是轉往國際學校&mdash;&mdash;英基往年輪候需三至四年，現在早一兩年已經有學位」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/JWD43LATFZH53NQLI5FHTHT6CI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FJWD43LATFZH53NQLI5FHTHT6CI%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Jvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=d7fd11c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FJWD43LATFZH53NQLI5FHTHT6CI%2F&h=4d88b993\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/JWD43LATFZH53NQLI5FHTHT6CI/</a>"},{"pid":"ae53fc334be2d68a6afe138c6d989292b8e1b0ee","tid":2487817,"uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:07:09.000Z","msg":"阿邊個：睇唔到留港讀書有何壞處，對退學預測難以理解"},{"pid":"0702d026eaecd0a422cf77ce485a38df409a2369","tid":2487817,"uid":284855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e132806f44166d85a43778b599df6f602378746e","tid":2487817,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:15:26.000Z","msg":"依家唔走, 唔通等香港俾美國cut埋個美元結算戶口先走咩"},{"pid":"7034b87f4a0b1032b7d82bdfb8213018890bdeef","tid":2487817,"uid":264158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0702d026eaecd0a422cf77ce485a38df409a2369","tid":2487817,"uid":284855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cfb4f0e166b94691f189adb52beeddc00e1a41","tid":2487817,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"學生是否在未來1至2年離港，確實會在面試部分計算在內<br />\n<br />\n你都on9，要簽生死狀呀而家"},{"pid":"66d2529e12d6749a9b334ba4633e064214ea0b42","tid":2487817,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"有錢唔走果d係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4020153be2d2f3ddd39864eb03c12193d98a042b","tid":2487817,"uid":264158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7cfb4f0e166b94691f189adb52beeddc00e1a41","tid":2487817,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"學生是否在未來1至2年離港，確實會在面試部分計算在內<br />\n<br />\n你都on9，要簽生死狀呀而家"},"citedBy":0,"